00:18:42.083 --> 00:18:43.917 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
The small bones.

286
00:18:44.917 --> 00:18:46.042 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
