He said<i> he </i>killed Sala.

288
00:18:49.917 --> 00:18:50.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah.

289
00:18:51.958 --> 00:18:53.083 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
It was his pit.

290
00:18:55.042 --> 00:18:57.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
